description._content: Description: Tanjong Unsang Lighthouse - No. 1. View of Foundation Excavation - Oct. 1922. Location: Tanjong Unsang, Borneo Date: October 1922 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Tanjong Unsang Lighthouse. View of Foundation Excavation - Photo shows line of demarcation between upper 3' compact sand, & lower layer of course well compacted sand mixed with coral boulders. - Oct. 1922. Location: Tanjong Unsang, Borneo Date: October 1922 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Tanjong Unsang Lighthouse - No 3. Side View of Pier - 300'ft. long. Oct. 1922. Location: Tanjong Unsang, Borneo Date: October 1922 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: Tanjong Unsang Lighthouse. View of temporary pier ready for laying track. - Oct. 1922. Location: Tanjong Unsang, Borneo Date: October 1922 ------------------------------------------------------ Description: No. 5. Tanjong Unsang Lighthouse. 31.5.23. Location: Tanjong Unsang, Borneo Date: 31 May 1923 ------------------------------------------------------ Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/517.
